summary: This mod replaces Skyrims woods and rocks.
descriptionHtml:
[IMG]http://i42.tinypic.com/2isft3q.jpg[/IMG]


[b][color=DarkOrange]This first version includes high res barks and tree stumps (No performance hit).  I will add barks for all texture sets,terrain clutter and details  in the next versions. All textures are completely build up from scratch. 

The next version will include the last parts of the basic set and will add the fall forest set.[/color][/b]

[url=http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=4863][b]Note: Works perfect with \"Better Landscape Skyrim\" by dirkduggler (My Brother)[/b][/url]
